Andrews v. Brewster et al. (Supreme Court, General Term, First Department. March 14, 1890.)

Argued before Van Brunt, P. J., and Brady and Daniels, JJ.

Wm. Allen Butler, for plaintiff. A. R. Byett, for defendant.

No opinion. Reargument ordered upon the question of damages. Por decision granting motion for new trial on exceptions, see ante, 114.
